body.text:

If this sounds like something you may be interested, can we please have a short call to discuss? What number can I reach you on?

Farhan

headline.text: Recruiter

Recruiter

elements.subject: Full Stack Engineer Opportunity - Global Investment Bank

body.text:
Hi Viktor, 

My name is Bill Fitzgerald, I'm a recruiter with the LPX Group, focusing on the financial services sector. I came across your profile and feel you would be a great fit for the Full Stack Developer role at a Global Investment Bank. 

The position is a full-time 6-month contract position located in NYC with a hybrid work structure. 

The role available is with the Asset Backed Product group (ABP) at a large international investment bank. They are looking for a Full Stack Engineer to help build and maintain internal software and tools for the ABP desk.  Responsibilities vary from improving and maintaining .NET desktop applications and APIs, developing web applications, setting and upgrading continuous delivery infrastructure and assisting traders and sales in their daily challenges including their excel spreadsheets.

Skills needed include:
	.NET C# preferably .NET Core and microservices
	Experience working with MVVM design pattern
	Experience working with a relational database (MSSQL, MySQL)
	Expertise in Web Services and Web API
	Client-side Web UI: Angular or similar
	Working knowledge of continuous delivery platform (Teamcity, Jenkins, etc)
	Previous experience working in Fixed Income Front office or Middle office
	Knowledge of Asset-backed products

Feel free to reach out to me directly (with resume and best contact number) if you or anyone you know would be interested in this position and I would be happy to discuss further.

Bill Fitzgerald
Recruiter
william.fitzgerald@leveluphcs.com
